    "Premise 2 of the argument is as follows:",
    "P2: If, by 2100, humanity is capable of building AI capable of permanently disempowering humanity, then AI capable of permanently disempowering humanity will be built by 2100.",
    "P2 is easy to explain.",
    "The antecedent of the conditional is P1, i.e., the view that humanity will, if it tries, build AI by 2100 which, if it tries, permanently disempowers humanity.",
    "The consequent is the claim that AI which will, if it tries, succeed at disempowering humanity will actually be built by 2100."
  ],
